=Episode 9=
(The Imperfect Best Friend)

15
00:02:01,820 --> 00:02:03,820
(Hotel Wednesday)

16
00:02:12,520 --> 00:02:13,880
She looks so sick.

17
00:02:13,880 --> 00:02:15,241
You sure we don't need
to bring her to a hospital?

18
00:02:16,200 --> 00:02:17,800
She's fine. She ate too much.

19
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:18,961
She has always been like this.

20
00:02:19,121 --> 00:02:20,161
You didn't eat anything just now.

21
00:02:20,161 --> 00:02:21,121
Let me buy something for you.

22
00:02:21,121 --> 00:02:22,401
No need. I'm not hungry.

23
00:02:22,961 --> 00:02:24,640
Just go back, Daqian. It's late now.

24
00:02:24,640 --> 00:02:25,681
I'll look after her.

25
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:27,401
I'll stay to keep you company.

26
00:02:27,800 --> 00:02:29,441
If something happens,
at least you'll have help.

27
00:02:41,320 --> 00:02:42,681
Daqian, sorry.

28
00:02:43,760 --> 00:02:45,281
I lent all my money

29
00:02:45,401 --> 00:02:46,600
to Dahua.

30
00:02:47,920 --> 00:02:49,040
It's okay.

31
00:02:49,200 --> 00:02:51,040
You have always been
a supportive friend.

32
00:02:51,441 --> 00:02:53,480
Whenever your friend has a problem,
you lend a hand.

33
00:02:54,080 --> 00:02:56,480
I'll find a solution for the shop.

34
00:03:09,750 --> 00:03:12,450
(Baihe Station)

35
00:03:13,320 --> 00:03:15,220
(Baihe Station, Entrance)

36
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:19,441
No need to see me off.

37
00:03:19,561 --> 00:03:20,640
It's cold out here.

38
00:03:20,640 --> 00:03:22,360
I can hail a cab to the train station.

39
00:03:25,841 --> 00:03:27,600
Cover yourself properly
if it's cold then.

40
00:03:31,880 --> 00:03:32,880
Once you return,

41
00:03:33,040 --> 00:03:34,561
find a proper job.

42
00:03:34,561 --> 00:03:35,320
All right?

43
00:03:35,640 --> 00:03:36,441
Yes.

44
00:03:37,480 --> 00:03:39,760
I'll pay you back as soon as possible.

45
00:03:40,161 --> 00:03:41,360
No worries. No rush.

46
00:03:42,920 --> 00:03:45,001
Daqian, thank you for last night.

47
00:03:45,200 --> 00:03:46,080
No need.

48
00:03:46,121 --> 00:03:47,961
