Gambling again?

62
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:48,920
It won't take too long.

63
00:04:49,360 --> 00:04:50,800
Dad, I don't think

64
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:52,360
I can buy the house at the moment.

65
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:53,240
I don't have enough money.

66
00:04:53,240 --> 00:04:54,360
Great.

67
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:56,120
I checked that spot. It's no good.

68
00:04:56,161 --> 00:04:58,000
Never do a losing business.

69
00:04:58,120 --> 00:04:59,000
You hope that I would never

70
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:00,641
buy that house, don't you?

71
00:05:01,321 --> 00:05:02,721
It's not that.

72
00:05:03,081 --> 00:05:04,161
You don't have enough money.

73
00:05:04,161 --> 00:05:05,440
