77
00:05:11,521 --> 00:05:13,841
I'm doing this for everyone.

78
00:05:14,281 --> 00:05:15,321
I'm running late.

79
00:05:15,721 --> 00:05:16,321
Bye.

80
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:05,920
You have a mean streak.

81
00:06:06,081 --> 00:06:07,721
No wonder your romance failed.

82
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:11,881
(Daqian?)

83
00:06:11,881 --> 00:06:13,161
Guan Zhe, it's me.

84
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:14,281
I need to have a talk with you.

85
00:06:15,201 --> 00:06:16,521
(I thought you wouldn't contact me)

86
00:06:16,521 --> 00:06:17,920
(after you left.)

87
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:20,161
(I'm not feeling myself recently.)

88
00:06:20,161 --> 00:06:21,600
(I was dying to get your news.)

89
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:22,800
(I wanted to contact you)

90
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:24,120
(but I didn't have the gut to.)

91
00:06:24,440 --> 00:06:26,401
(I could hardly sleep
at night these few months.)

92
00:06:26,680 --> 00:06:28,401
You miss me so much
that you can't sleep?

93
00:06:29,560 --> 00:06:30,440
Me too.

94
00:06:31,161 --> 00:06:33,161
Whenever I think about you,
sleep eludes me.

95
00:06:33,961 --> 00:06:35,961
(I didn't expect that you still love me.)

96
00:06:35,961 --> 00:06:37,401
Don't get ahead of yourself.

97
00:06:37,401 --> 00:06:39,560
You couldn't sleep because all the
bad things you did haunt you.

98
00:06:39,881 --> 00:06:40,680
(Daqian.)

99
00:06:41,081 --> 00:06:42,480
(I did hurt you.)

100
00:06:42,480 --> 00:06:44,440
(But I also hurt myself in the process.)

101
00:06:44,521 --> 00:06:46,440
(After the breakup, I couldn't sleep.
I couldn't eat.)

102
00:06:46,440 --> 00:06:47,881
(I'm suffering too.)

103
00:06:48,480 --> 00:06:49,240
I'll claim

104
00:06:49,240 --> 00:06:50,761
the moral damage from you in the future.

105
00:06:50,761 --> 00:06:51,961
Remember the 60,000 yuan you owe me?

106
00:06:51,961 --> 00:06:52,841
Give it back

107
00:06:52,881 --> 00:06:53,680
within these two days.

108
00:06:54,721 --> 00:06:56,240
(You're not Zheng Daqian.)

109
00:06:56,240 --> 00:06:57,560
(You are using my ex-girlfriend's voice)

110
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:58,641
(to scam me.)

111
00:06:58,641 --> 00:07:00,521
(I'll call the police now.)

112
00:07:00,800 --> 00:07:02,040
If I'm not Zheng Daqian,

