129
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:14,161
What are you trying to do?

130
00:08:14,161 --> 00:08:15,401
Is it because of the breakup?

131
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:17,281
It has nothing to do with it.

132
00:08:17,440 --> 00:08:18,560
I just want to earn some money.

133
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:19,161
Wait.

134
00:08:19,321 --> 00:08:20,000
Zheng Daqian.

135
00:08:20,920 --> 00:08:23,560
I overlooked an important detail.

136
00:08:23,761 --> 00:08:24,920
You just broke up.

137
00:08:25,240 --> 00:08:26,440
Your female hormone

138
00:08:26,440 --> 00:08:28,000
is in imbalance.

139
00:08:28,281 --> 00:08:30,040
When you have nothing to do,
you become sentimental.

140
00:08:30,040 --> 00:08:32,600
So you have to do something.

141
00:08:33,081 --> 00:08:34,800
