145
00:08:41,800 --> 00:08:42,521
(Hey.)

146
00:08:42,881 --> 00:08:43,761
(Daqian.)

147
00:08:44,080 --> 00:08:45,640
(Where are you? I want to find you.)

148
00:08:45,641 --> 00:08:46,800
Zheng Daqian.

149
00:08:46,800 --> 00:08:48,680
