152
00:08:52,161 --> 00:08:54,401
Regardless of the reason,
you shouldn't contact him.

153
00:08:54,401 --> 00:08:56,361
He just has to sweet talk you
and you're all smitten.

154
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:58,161
You are the typical

155
00:08:58,161 --> 00:08:59,680
victim who enables

156
00:08:59,680 --> 00:09:00,840
her captor.

157
00:09:00,840 --> 00:09:01,881
