158
00:09:04,881 --> 00:09:05,641
You...

159
00:09:06,161 --> 00:09:07,241
You know what?

160
00:09:07,241 --> 00:09:09,361
Why not consider Yan?

161
00:09:09,560 --> 00:09:11,001
