199
00:12:22,161 --> 00:12:22,960
She doesn't.

200
00:12:22,960 --> 00:12:23,680
I'm just staying for a few days.

201
00:12:23,680 --> 00:12:24,761
No need to bother her.

202
00:12:24,761 --> 00:12:26,560
You know what?
Let's eat together tonight.

203
00:12:26,560 --> 00:12:27,521
I'll call her.

204
00:12:27,521 --> 00:12:28,161
Don't.

205
00:12:29,080 --> 00:12:30,680
I have plans with friends.
I have to go now.

206
00:12:30,720 --> 00:12:31,521
See you.

207
00:12:32,161 --> 00:12:34,080
Dahua, stay safe.

208
00:12:34,080 --> 00:12:35,881
See you next time!

209
00:12:54,080 --> 00:12:55,121
Mr. Zheng, you're back.

210
00:12:55,361 --> 00:12:56,960
What's the good news?

211
00:13:07,080 --> 00:13:07,720
Mi Lan.

212
00:13:08,960 --> 00:13:10,521
Don't you think
something's wrong with my dad?

213
00:13:11,161 --> 00:13:13,361
No. He seems cheery.

214
00:13:14,121 --> 00:13:15,840
I will follow him tonight.

215
00:13:16,200 --> 00:13:17,481
I think he's up to something.

216
00:13:17,920 --> 00:13:18,761
What?

217
00:13:19,040 --> 00:13:20,601
During the day when no one was home,

218
00:13:20,601 --> 00:13:22,320
I saw him going through my mom's bag

219
00:13:22,320 --> 00:13:23,960
and he took her credit card.

220
00:13:24,200 --> 00:13:25,440
Maybe he

221
00:13:25,440 --> 00:13:27,440
wanted to buy something.

222
00:13:27,720 --> 00:13:29,040
Nothing good will come of it
if he's doing it behind my mom's back.

223
00:13:31,241 --> 00:13:33,320
I also ran into Dahua
in the mahjong house.

224
00:13:35,161 --> 00:13:36,440
