225
00:13:36,720 --> 00:13:38,040
She said she missed the train.

226
00:13:38,200 --> 00:13:39,641
I invited her to eat together tonight

227
00:13:39,641 --> 00:13:40,720
but she turned me down

228
00:13:40,720 --> 00:13:42,080
and ran away.

229
00:13:45,361 --> 00:13:46,601
I should pay her a visit

230
00:13:46,601 --> 00:13:47,840
to find out what's going on.

231
00:14:45,641 --> 00:14:46,440
Password?

232
00:14:51,241 --> 00:14:52,281
8888.

233
00:15:01,040 --> 00:15:02,080
My birthday?

